# File Organization & Structure

**NEVER create new files unnecessarily:**
- Search existing code first (grep/search in [scripts/shared/](mdc:scripts/shared/), [types/](mdc:types/))
- Extend existing files when functionality fits
- Only create for genuinely new concepts or >500 line files

**NEVER use "Unified" or "Consolidated" in file names**

**Code locations:**
- Utilities → [scripts/shared/](mdc:scripts/shared/)
- Types → [types/](mdc:types/) (barrel export from [index.ts](mdc:types/index.ts))
- Deployment → [scripts/](mdc:scripts/)
- Config → [config/](mdc:config/)
- Contracts → [contracts/src/](mdc:contracts/src/)
- Apps → [apps/{app-name}/](mdc:apps/)

**Monorepo structure:**
```
jeju/
├── apps/          # agent, bazaar, gateway, indexer, leaderboard
├── config/        # base-networks.json, jeju-tokens.json, chain/
├── contracts/     # src/, script/, test/
├── scripts/       # deploy-*.ts, shared/
├── types/         # chain.ts, contracts.ts, defi.ts, infrastructure.ts
└── vendor/
```

**Import patterns:**
```typescript
import { ChainConfig, NetworkType } from '../types'; // Central types
import { Logger, FailoverProvider } from './shared'; // Barrel exports
```

**Networks:** localnet (8545), testnet (Base Sepolia), mainnet (Base)
